findings.title: Out of gas
findings.description: Functions includeInReward(), _getCurrentSupply, and addToBlackList() may abort with OUT_OF_GAS exception if there are long lists.

findings.title: Owner privileges (In the period when the owner is not renounced)
findings.description: The contract owner has excessive privileges to change fees, maximum transaction amount, remove addresses from blacklist, and modify other critical settings.
